<p class="MsoNormal">
<img alt="" height="347" src="includes/sub_content/img/30825.jpg" width="733" /></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 22.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">安省提名投资移民计划</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 22.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<font face="宋体">（</font>ontario immigration nominee program<font face="宋体">，简称</font><font face="Calibri">OINP)</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><o:p>
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<font face="宋体">安省投资移民新政策</font>3<font face="宋体">大亮点：</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
1<font face="宋体">、最低投资额大幅降低，安省外</font><font face="Calibri">50</font><font face="宋体">万加币起投资；（安省内企业</font><font face="Calibri">100</font><font face="宋体">万加币起）</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
2<font face="宋体">、先工签后移民</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
3<font face="宋体">、语言可以过来学</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><o:p>
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: rgb(192,0,0); font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<font face="宋体">申请人首先获得两年工签支持，实施商业计划，同时提高语言能力，申请人只要在申请提名时达到</font>CLB5<font face="宋体">的程度即可。</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><o:p>
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<font face="宋体">安省企业家移民：</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">1、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">如果企业可以促进安省经济的发展，那么企业家可以申请短期工签，以便获得永久居民的身份。</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">2、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">每个题名人至少投资</font>50<font face="宋体">万加币购买或者建立企业，依据投资区域与领域不同；</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">3、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">每个题名人至少</font>80<font face="宋体">至</font><font face="Calibri">150</font><font face="宋体">万加币净资产，根据投资区域与领域不同；</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">4、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">如有需要，企业家的一名合作伙伴也可以提民；（就是可以代一名伙伴）</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">5、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">在提名永久居民前，企业家</font>/<font face="宋体">或合作伙伴需要在两年内达到这项计划的最低标准（包括语言）</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">6、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">给加拿大公民或永久居民创造至少</font>2<font face="宋体">个全职工作</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><o:p>
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>


<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<font face="宋体">公司投资移民：</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">1、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">向安省现有企业或初创业最少投资</font>500<font face="宋体">万加币；</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">2、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">提名员工当前应该在该公司任职，并且对安省地区业务的发展很关键；</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">3、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">每个提名均需要给加拿大公民或永久居民创造至少</font>5<font face="宋体">个全职工作；</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><![if !supportLists]>
<span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<span style="mso-list: Ignore;">4、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">在提名永久居民前，提名员工应在两年时间内达到最低与要要求；</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; background: rgb(255,0,0); mso-highlight: rgb(255,0,0);"><font face="宋体">（几个可以几个人合作办理这个项目）</font><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><o:p>
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><o:p>
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b>
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<font face="宋体">加拿大伟力集团：</font> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;905-604-5622<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b>
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<font face="宋体">加拿大伟力集团传真：</font> &nbsp;905-604-5922<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b>
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><o:p>
&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b>
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
<font face="宋体">中国直播加拿大总部电话：</font>950-405-99368<font face="宋体">，</font><font face="Times New Roman">905-405-93039</font><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b>
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">
